SHORTCUT "Open Developer bookmarks"
ACTION comment WFCommentActionText="Opens the bookmarks for Developer in Xcode."
ACTION comment WFCommentActionText="This shortcut uses a technique I learned from Mattt Thompson to open a specific bookmark set in Xcode.\n\nThis is useful for me because I have a lot of bookmarks in Xcode for Developer, and I want to quickly open the same group every time I work on that project."
ACTION openapp WFAppIdentifier="com.apple.dt.Xcode" WFSelectedApp={"BundleIdentifier": "com.apple.dt.Xcode", "Name": "Xcode", "TeamIdentifier": "0000000000"}
ACTION runapplescript WFAppleScript="on run {input, parameters}\ttell application \"Xcode\"\t\ttell application \"System Events\"\t\t\tkeystroke \"\\#\" using {command down}\t\tend tell\tend tell\treturn inputend run"
